BT 1 0 0 1 0 39 Tm 12 TL /F1 9 Tf 0 0 0 rg (A QuTiP simulation of Bell state entanglement under independent dephasing reveals a result that appears to violate the) Tj T* (Wike Coherence Law: at decoherence rates where single-qubit coherence survives at 100%, two-qubit entanglement) Tj T* (collapses ) Tj /F2 9 Tf (instantly) Tj /F1 9 Tf ( to zero. The concurrence C\(20\) = 0.000000 at both gentle \(gamma = 0.005\) and harsh \(gamma =) Tj T* (0.0804\) dephasing -- 0% survival -- while the individual qubits at identical gamma maintain full coherence.) Tj T* ET
